Jaysen MCCLEARY, Plaintiff-Appellant,
v.
CITY OF DES MOINES and Jerry Schillinger, Defendants-Appellees. No. 17-1992 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed January 9, 2019

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION See Iowa R. App. P. 6.904

Jaysen McCleary appeals the dismissal of his application for contempt. AFFIRMED.

AFFIRMED.
